                <note type="abstract" xml:lang="en" source="#bib2500-7">A two-part universal history composed originally by <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/239">Bar Hebraeus</persName> and 
                    continued by later authors. <bibl>Part 1<ptr target="http://syriaca.org/work/2501"/>
                    </bibl> deals with secular history and <bibl>Part 2<ptr target="http://syriaca.org/work/2502"/>
                    </bibl> 
                    with church history. For editions and translations, see the bibliography of each of these parts, which have been published separately.</note>
                
                
                <!--<note xml:lang="syr" type="prologue" source="#bib2500-1">
